{"tid":1134864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心喺旺角增值俾人偷錢！","createTime":"2019-05-02T03:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T04:02:45.000Z","uid":10001,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ad68e0e82c4321cc5f5163009ef9ed5c36fce212","tid":1134864,"uid":10001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"話說件事係發生喺我屋企人身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日，我呀媽喺旺角約咗幾個fd食飯。<br />\n<br />\n當時呀媽用八達通出閘就顯示負錢，理所當然就去左附近增值機增值。<br />\n<br />\n咁呀媽唔太識用個新款增值機，所以就睇住指示慢慢㩒，入左三張五十蚊㩒confirm嗰陣，有條友突然衝出嚟㩒個mon，我呀媽俾佢嚇親，鬧咗條友一句痴線就走咗。<br />\n<br />\n到食完飯喺旺角搭返屋企先發現仲係負錢，原來嗰條友喺我呀媽㩒confirm嗰下㩒咗cancel，我呀媽冇為意，以為增咗值又俾個痴線佬嚇親，所以都冇check就離開咗。<br />\n<br />\n嗰條友由出閘跟住我呀媽尾到增值機，話唔定係專吼啲師奶仔，喺出閘位聽到佢地負錢就跟佢尾，再咁樣偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位記住小心啲，check清楚係增好值先走人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f58962920d9695e1ed8c0b0f9ae200f682c541","tid":1134864,"uid":132902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"伯母真係唔好彩"},{"pid":"f2688db12cfc33a47b740db3b432f07c1a4678aa","tid":1134864,"uid":10001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f58962920d9695e1ed8c0b0f9ae200f682c541","tid":1134864,"uid":132902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"伯母真係唔好彩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係增500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2202e8d5b52961d64abc6b1623a585da609c3613","tid":1134864,"uid":147292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"負錢點搭地鐵返去？"},{"pid":"13c8cd715eef891fccd0e03268ce3e74c86de2de","tid":1134864,"uid":225760,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7da4c2a9e